### Maven ###
target/

### IntelliJ IDEA ###
# IntelliJ project files are user/machine-specific. Letting them travel
# in git causes things like stale "JVM target 5" overrides in compiler.xml
# that break teammates' builds when they pull. Each developer should let
# IntelliJ regenerate these from pom.xml on first import.
.idea/
*.iml
out/
!**/src/main/**/out/
!**/src/test/**/out/
.kotlin

### Eclipse ###
.apt_generated
.classpath
.factorypath
.project
.settings
.springBeans
.sts4-cache
bin/
!**/src/main/**/bin/
!**/src/test/**/bin/

